{"tid":2038583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宜家正式係到號召所有黃既Youtuber kol全部停止更新IG FB一個月","createTime":"2020-05-27T15:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T16:25:06.000Z","uid":150536,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"75d432a878634f928ee632f2bf8166b82baac63b","tid":2038583,"uid":150536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"希望所有黃既 Youtuber kol 停止更新IG FB一個月。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然商業既廣告/更新佢要你放係Facebook同Instagram就唔影響，始終都係各位同路人既其中一樣收入來源。<br />\n主要係希望各位將一啲個人既更新轉到Twitter，令到更多人慢慢用多啲Twitter。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個月之後再視乎情況，兩邊一齊更新定係全面轉用 Twitter 由各位自行決定。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n民族自強，香港獨立。"},{"pid":"3a5e493585b336a47eb686d5f94cef92340384c1","tid":2038583,"uid":150536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:53:19.000Z","msg":"叫香港人玩Twitter原來一直係錯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2038288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2038288</a><br />\n<br />\n放棄twitter做任 將twitter變成另一個Facebook/Instagram<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2038338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2038338</a>"},{"pid":"8f70d674e78578f5f5688e65f3d84aa71c3e9805","tid":2038583,"uid":150536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"100fdce85196069630e02b162efca6e567613f62","tid":2038583,"uid":150536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e84e14ea775e2ae37ae434a96d9966818bd2f253","tid":2038583,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"你今日#boycottchinagoods未呀<br />\n<br />\n港共立國安法唔畀我哋搞黃色經濟圈，我哋就將黃色經濟圈發展去全世界，boycott china goods<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fxesrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fxesrS</a>"},{"pid":"2